17. A method comprising the steps of: 
providing a medical balloon with at least one position marker thereon; 
providing a catheter for mounting the balloon thereon; 
aligning the position marker with a desired portion of the catheter so as to position the balloon; and 
bonding the balloon to the catheter.

19. The method of claim 18 further comprising the steps of: 
providing a medical device; 
aligning the medical device with the position marker on the balloon.

22. A method comprising the steps of: 
providing a catheter with a medical balloon mounted thereon, the medical balloon having at least one position marker thereon; 
providing a medical device for disposing about the balloon; 
disposing the medical device about the balloon; 
aligning and positioning the medical device with respect to the position marker in a desired position about the balloon.
